First Bank System Inc said it hasfound a potential buyer for First Bank Luverne and its officein Pipestone, Minnesota.    The bank holding company said 215 Holding Co, a corporationcontrolled by the family of the late Robert Short, will buyFirst Bank Luverne. The bank has 59.2 mln dlrs in assets.    First Bank, which announced plans in 1985 to restructureits banking assets by offering to sell 28 of its banks with atotal of 45 offices, said agreements have now been signed for43 of these offices. Reuter&#3;